humbUrl":"https://c-p.rmcdn.net/5479c8026bbe3ca75cc0a82e/1590115/upload-c44c408d-c54c-4570-a612-7afee5ca98ff.jpg","url":"https://c-p.rmcdn.net/5479c8026bbe3ca75cc0a82e/1590115/upload-e7f3f90f-1f9a-41be-af52-e7bdb369a0fa.jpg","type":"jpg","unscaledUrl":"https://c-p.rmcdn.net/5479c8026bbe3ca75cc0a82e/1590115/upload-e7f3f90f-1f9a-41be-af52-e7bdb369a0fa.jpg","final2xUrl":"https://c-p.rmcdn.net/5479c8026bbe3ca75cc0a82e/3936815/Image-ede57623-a91c-49d5-bfee-00acf9e99630.jpg","finalUrl":"https://c-p.rmcdn.net/5479c8026bbe3ca75cc0a82e/3936815/Image-8f5a967c-8ffd-45e4-8423-9407ff4c328f.jpg","unscaledOptimizedUrl":"https://c-p.rmcdn.net/5479c8026bbe3ca75cc0a82e/3936815/Image-4a88dfc0-ef8f-424d-a777-87b54839b4d8.jpg"},"cropW":3050,"cropH":3812,"cropX":0,"cropY":0,"originalW":3050,"originalH":3812,"scale":0.094426229508197,"pic_opacity":1,"border_size":0,"border_color":"ffffff","border_radius":0,"border_radius_max":false,"opacity":1,"x":560,"y":1205,"w":288,"h":360,"z":312,"angle":270,"flip_v":true},"viewport_tablet_portrait":{},"__v":0},{"_id":"631f02bce633ea002e7847ae","wid":"631f02bce633ea002e7847ae","mag_num_id":3936815,"type":"text","x":0,"y":1317,"w":422,"h":504,"version":3,"z":304,"name":"","bgColor":"ffffff00","blocks":[{"key":"fgq4o","text":"\"Dasha Glukhova makes areal photography. It doesn’t mean she does photoshots in the air (although that happens, too). It’s just that all her pictures are full of air.","entityRanges":[],"depth":0},{"key":"1efd1","text":" ","entityRanges":[],"depth":0},{"key":"b6p8v","text":"Dasha is the master of capturing the moment. But many photographers are. Unlike them, she’s capturing something so rapid you never know if it even lasted at all.","entityRanges":[],"depth":0},{"key":"7mtj3","text":"Although the approach is artistic, you can definitely spot the realism of the artist. When she shows the hidden glow of things, it’s non-retouched and unenhanced. The ephemeral reality, the transience of being, the light and the air. That’s some of the keywords of Dasha Glukhova’s photography you experience as a viewer\". \n\n(c) Diana Windsdorm","entityRanges":[],"depth":0},{"key":"fp89m","text":"\n                       ","entityRanges":[],"depth":0}],"blocksMeta":[{"key":"fgq4o","data":{"textStyle":"style-6ce43b59-2a09-4c16-b026-d1e97113fd32"}},{"key":"1efd1","data":{"textStyle":"style-6ce43b59-2a09-4c16-b026-d1e97113fd32"}},{"key":"b6p8v","data":{"textStyle":"style-6ce43b59-2a09-4c16-b026-d1e97113fd32"}},{"key":"7mtj3","data":{"textStyle":"style-6ce43b59-2a09-4c16-b026-d1e97113fd32"}},{"key":"fp89m","data":{"textStyle":"style-6ce43b59-2a09-4c16-b026-d1e97113fd32"}}],"columns":{"count":1,"gap":16},"styles":[{"key":"fgq4o","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"1efd1","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"b6p8v","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"7mtj3","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"fp89m","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}}],"verticalAlign":"top","viewport_phone_portrait":{"styles":[{"key":"fgq4o","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"1efd1","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"b6p8v","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"7mtj3","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}},{"key":"fp89m","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[],"keys":[],"values":[]}}],"bgColor":"ffffff00","columns":{"count":1,"gap":16},"blocksMeta":[{"key":"fgq4o","data":{"textStyle":"paragraph-cc86f006-f290-4885-8700-d1d7101cd5a5"}},{"key":"1efd1","data":{"textStyle":"paragraph-cc86f006-f290-4885-8700-d1d7101cd5a5"}},{"key":"b6p8v","data":{"textStyle":"paragraph-cc86f006-f290-4885-8700-d1d7101cd5a5"}},{"key":"7mtj3","data":{"textStyle":"paragraph-cc86f006-f290-4885-8700-d1d7101cd5a5"}},{"key